# Ranking algorithm

**Binary insertion sort** — insert each new song via binary search on the sorted list using **pairwise** “which do you prefer?” comparisons.

- **Pros**: Clear UX; ~O(n log n) comparisons when choices are consistent; ~⌈log₂(n)⌉ steps per insertion.
- **Cons**: More comparisons per song than quaternary bucketing; warn users above threshold (25+) informally only.
- **UI**: `BinaryPlacementView` + `SongCompareCard`; no 4-bucket placement screen.

See `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` for modules and edge cases.
